                </h2>
                <p class="text-violet-100 mb-6">
                    See how your education affects your BC PNP score.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/bc-pnp-calculator"
                    class="inline-block bg-white text-violet-700 font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-violet-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    Use the Calculator ‚Üí
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</BaseLayout>
